{"tid":1521822,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請扺制Mtr旗下嘅商場","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:48:09.000Z","uid":9214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be91a1e99142debabcb734709ed57397f12819ce","tid":1521822,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:00:44.000Z","msg":"黨鐵佔收入4成<br />\n其如六成都係物業收租<br />\n除左跳閘大家快啲罷買或者得閒去開下party la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7FS39L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7FS39L.png&h=e6737792&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef6e856567c01ded17d757697aff3195a829b8e","tid":1521822,"uid":139282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"63f118854a7df1bfd0608d050223793e092458a8","tid":1521822,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvQ0tCb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvQ0tCb.jpg&h=a007445d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d30cb2a6971874d4da311e4a029319890550d9eb","tid":1521822,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvbbCbn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvbbCbn.jpg&h=9db17b60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d56c71e3b2b76a9f6e74e2ea655610911de1282c","tid":1521822,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"唔購物"}]}